==German==
===Etymology===
Old High German ''[[heriberga]]'', compound of ''[[Heer]]'' and a derivation of ''[[bergen]]'', literally "accomodation for the army". Related to ''[[harbour]]'' and ''[[harbinger]]''.
===Noun===
'''Herberge''' ''f'' (''pl'' '''Herbergen''')

# [[hospice]], [[hostel]]

